PowerColor原來是[[ATI|ATI]]顯示卡的授權製造商，亦即ATI的AIC合作夥伴；ATI被[[AMD|AMD]]收購以後繼承原來的身份，現時為AMD的AIC合作廠商。然而，PowerColor亦以「Zogis」品牌製造[[NVIDIA|NVIDIA]]的[[顯示卡|顯示卡]]。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.theinquirer.net/default.aspx?article=34404 |title=Power Color USA does Nvidia - The Inquirer<!-- Bot generated title --> |accessdate=2013-05-04 |archive-date=2006-09-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20060926003723/http://www.theinquirer.net/default.aspx?article=34404 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.nvidia.com/object/IO_35375.html |title=Press Release<!-- Bot generated title --> |accessdate=2013-05-04 |archive-date=2013-03-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130317210700/http://www.nvidia.com/object/IO_35375.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name=autogenerated2>{{cite web |url=http://www.power-color.com/club/ |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2013-05-04 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080430012409/http://power-color.com/club/ |archivedate=2008-04-30 }}</ref>PowerColor大部分的顯示卡實際是由[[富士康|富士康]]代工生產。<ref name=autogenerated1>{{Cite web |url=http://www.theinquirer.net/?article=12997 |title=Why PowerColor Radeons are different to ATI Radeons - The Inquirer<!-- Bot generated title --> |accessdate=2013-05-04 |archive-date=2015-02-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150214115451/http://www.theinquirer.net/?article=12997 |dead-url=no }}</ref> 

PowerColor的顯示卡產品主要使用AMD/ATI[[顯示核心|顯示核心]]，從入門級消費產品和低階[[工作站|工作站]]平台，到高階遊戲電腦都有產品對應。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.theinquirer.net/?article=16470 |title=Powercolor range stands out from the graphics crowd - The Inquirer<!-- Bot generated title --> |accessdate=2013-05-04 |archive-date=2005-03-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20050318171152/http://www.theinquirer.net/?article=16470 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.powercolor.com/eng/Products.asp |title=Welcome to the PowerColor World - Products<!-- Bot generated title --> |accessdate=2013-05-04 |archive-date=2010-03-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100304084125/http://www.powercolor.com/eng/products.asp |dead-url=no }}</ref>PowerColor的板卡製造業務主要由[[富士康|富士康]]承接，使得PowerColor有更多的精力去研發和改進顯示卡的板卡設計，可以在AMD/ATI授權製造公版顯示卡的同時可以開發出更節能的版本，或規格和效能比公版設計更高的[[超頻|超頻]]版/高時脈版本的顯示卡，和PowerColor情況類似的AMD合作廠商還有[[藍寶科技|藍寶科技]]。<ref name=autogenerated1 />

PowerColor的產品還在[[個人電腦|個人電腦]]硬體業界屢獲獎項。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.powercolor.com/au/Awards.asp |title=Welcome to the PowerColor World - Awards<!-- Bot generated title --> |accessdate=2013-05-04 |archive-date=2013-04-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130424134608/http://powercolor.com/au/awards.asp |dead-url=no }}</ref>除了顯示卡以外，PowerColor也提供電腦[[機殼|機殼]]、[[電源供應器|電源供應器]]等設備。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.powercolor.com/Tw/default.asp |title=PowerColor Official Website - Graphics, Cases, Power Supply |accessdate=2013-05-04 |archive-date=2013-05-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130505004900/http://powercolor.com/Tw/default.asp |dead-url=no }}</ref>

